	No longer passed ControlButtons & or Dialogs &.
	(bc): new method, enabling the daughter classes to access the
	ButtonController.
	(C_FormBaseApplyCB):
	(C_FormBaseOKCB):
	(C_FormBaseCancelCB):
	(C_FormBaseRestoreCB):
	(C_WMHideCB): changes due to a change in the ViewBase class.

