	as MinipageParams::pageWidth.

2002-01-14	Martin Vermeer <martin.vermeer@hut.fi>

	* FormMathsBitmap.C:
	  FormMathsPanel.C:
	  MathsSymbols.C: Blackboard Bold and Calligraphic std symbols
	added to math panel's 'misc' sub-panel.

